<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694258>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A, B—Aspitates forbesi; C–F—A. kozhantchikovi; G, H—A. taylorae; I, J—A. obscurata; K, L—Siona lineata; M, N—Cleora cinctaria. A, E, G, I, K, M—genital segment; B–D, F, H, J, L, N—phallos, C, D—process of phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694310>
    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A—Siona lineata; B—Cleora cinctaria; C—Ascotis selenaria; D— Ectropis crepuscularia; E—Parectropis similaria; F—Aethalura punctulata. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694310/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

